Epic Dragon	CATEGORY:Internal	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Epic Dragon ~ Spells	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Epic Dragon ~ Spell-Like Abilities	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Epic Dragon ~ Improved Spell Capacity	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Epic Dragon ~ Empower Spell-Like Abilities	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Epic Dragon ~ Maximize Spell-Like Abilities	
Spells	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:A dragon knows and casts arcane spells as a sorcerer of the level indicated in its variety description, gaining bonus spells for a high Charisma score. Some dragons can also cast spells from the cleric list or cleric domain lists as arcane spells.	KEY:Epic Dragon ~ Spells																												SOURCEPAGE:Elh
Spell-Like Abilities	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:A dragon's spelllike abilities depend on its age and variety. It gains the abilities indicated for its age plus all previous ones. Its age category or its sorcerer caster level, whichever is higher, is the caster level for these abilities. The save DC is 10 + dragon's Cha modifier + spell level. All spell-like abilities are usable once per day unless otherwise noted.	KEY:Epic Dragon ~ Spell-Like Abilities																												SOURCEPAGE:Elh
Improved Spell Capacity	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:An epic dragon with a caster level above 20th gains the Improved Spell Capacity feat as a bonus feat once for every three caster levels above 20th.	KEY:Epic Dragon ~ Improved Spell Capacity							BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Dragon Improved Spell Capacity|(DragonSpellcasterLVL-20)/3																					SOURCEPAGE:Elh	
Empower Spell-Like Abilities	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:An epic dragon can apply the Empower Spell feat to one of its spell-like abilities that it can use at least twice per day. If the dragon has limited use of the spell-like ability (3/day, for example), the empowered ability uses up two uses of the ability. If the dragon can use the ability at will, there is no cost for empowering the ability. The dragon does not need to specify a spell-like ability when it chooses this feat; it can apply the feat to any spell-like ability it possesses.	KEY:Epic Dragon ~ Empower Spell-Like Abilities																												SOURCEPAGE:Elh	
Maximize Spell-Like Abilities	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RaceAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:The dragon can apply the Maximize Spell feat to one of its spell-like abilities that it can use at least three times per day. If the dragon has limited use of the spell-like ability (3/day, for example), the maximized ability uses up three uses of the ability. If the dragon can use the ability at will, there is no cost for maximizing the ability. The dragon does not need to specify a spell-like ability when it chooses this feat; it can apply the feat to any spell-like ability it possesses.	KEY:Epic Dragon ~ Maximize Spell-Like Abilities																												SOURCEPAGE:Elh	

